      "actionDesc": "Reported to House",
      "text": "<p><strong>SBA Fraud Enforcement Extension Act</strong></p><p>This bill extends the statute of limitations to 10&nbsp;years for fraud-based criminal and civil offenses with respect to the Shuttered Venue Operators Grant and the Restaurant Revitalization Fund&nbsp;COVID-19 relief programs.</p>",
